        <mxCell id="auth-middleware" value="2. authMiddleware.js&#xa;• Extract JWT from header&#xa;• jwt.verify(token, SECRET)&#xa;• Load user from DB&#xa;• Check user.isActive&#xa;• Attach req.user" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffc107;strokeColor=#ff6f00;fontSize=9;shadow=1;" vertex="1" parent="lane-api">
