        <mxCell id="legend-colors" value="Color Meanings:&#xa;• Green: User actions, success states&#xa;• Blue: API calls, backend routes&#xa;• Purple: Services (execution, AI, atomic)&#xa;• Red Cylinders: Database operations&#xa;• Orange Ellipses: WebSocket events&#xa;• Cyan: External systems (Playwright, AI APIs)&#xa;• Gray/Brown: File system operations&#xa;• Yellow: Decisions, conditions&#xa;• Red: Errors, failures, critical paths&#xa;• Light Green: Webhooks, notifications" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
