        <mxCell id="metadata-content" value="Flow Name: Single Test Execution Flow&#xa;Scope: User → API → Execution → Reporting → Notification&#xa;&#xa;Services Involved:&#xa;• executionService.js (orchestrator)&#xa;• allureEnrichmentService.js (reporting)&#xa;• globalAIService.js (AI analysis)&#xa;• webhookService.js (notifications)&#xa;• atomicFlowSaveService.js (data persistence)&#xa;&#xa;Database Tables:&#xa;• TestRun (execution record)&#xa;• TestRunStep (step-by-step results)&#xa;• TestAsset (screenshots, videos, traces)&#xa;• Deviation (AI failure analysis)&#xa;• AuditLog (compliance tracking)&#xa;&#xa;API Endpoints:&#xa;• POST /api/flows/:id/run (primary)&#xa;&#xa;WebSocket Events:&#xa;• execution:started&#xa;• step:completed (loop)&#xa;• ai:analysis:complete&#xa;• execution:completed&#xa;&#xa;Real-time: WebSocket (socket.io)&#xa;Last Updated: 2025-12-12&#xa;Complexity: Expert Grade (150+ nodes, 8 swim lanes)&#xa;Expected Duration: 30s - 5 minutes&#xa;Industry Pattern: GitHub Actions, CircleCI, Jenkins" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=9;" vertex="1" parent="1">
